    "created_at": "2016-01-29T23:04:39Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-01-29T23:04:39Z",
    "body": "I had a look at the solution for hiding mentioned in https://github.com/atom/electron/issues/3694 but that doesn't work in the case where the app is a menubar-only app without a menu. In this case, even pressing `cmd-H` doesn't hide the app so it really needs an api call for it.\n"
